                <a href='http://www.salon.com/2014/09/20/cut_it_out_atheists_why_its_time_to_stop_behaving_like_bill_maher_and_richard_dawkins/' class="gaTrackLinkEvent" data-ga-track-json="[&quot;navigation&quot;, &quot;click&quot;, &quot;mostread&quot;]" title='Cut it out, atheists! Why it&#039;s time to stop behaving like Bill Maher and Richard Dawkins'>
