                <h4>Photos from the Happy Ending Salon</h4>
                <p class='slideTitle'></p>
                <p>On Wednesday, September 10th Amanda Stern partnered with Salon to relaunch <a href="http://amandastern.com/happyending/">The Happy Ending Music and Reading Series</a>. We had the pleasure of hosting authors <a href="http://www.lesliejamison.com/">Leslie Jamison</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/zadiesmithauthor">Zadie Smith</a>, and <a href="http://authors.simonandschuster.com/Matthew-Thomas/427003006">Matthew Thomas</a>, artist <a href="http://www.edwinawhite.com/">Edwina White</a>, and musician <a href="http://www.emilywellsmusic.com/">Emily Wells</a>. <a href="http://www.moleskine.com/us/">Moleskine</a>, <a href="http://greenlightbookstore.com/">Greenlight Bookstore</a>, and <a href="http://plymouthgin.com/age.php">Plymouth Gin</a> were event partners.</p>
                
                
